{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:02:56.181694509Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"1. **Wrong config keys for script steps**: The handler was looking for `step.Config[\"command\"]` and `step.Config[\"script\"]`, but the DSL uses `\"run\"` as the config key. Script steps like `run = \"go test ./...\"` would never match, returning 404 instead of showing the command content.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:02:56.181697364Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:02:56.181702894Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"2. **Missing fallback for inline prompt text**: When a prompt value wasn't a file reference (or the file read failed), the handler fell through to the 404 error instead of writing the prompt text as inline content.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:02:56.181705249Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:02:56.181708495Z"}
